Description: Up for sale is my G&L ASAT Special USA Fullerton Deluxe in Flamed Honey Burst in Like New Condition. Bought this new about 5 years ago and have played it only half a dozen times or so. Everything is just the way it came from the factory and the instrument is in immaculate condition. Just look at the pictures to appreciate what a beautiful instrument this is. I can only say that it plays as good as it looks. No dents, no dings, no buckle rash, no fret wear. Sale includes Case, Certificate of Authenticity (signed by Leo Fender's wife), Original Sales Receipt, Warranty Statement, and Original Case Candy. Selling to thin the herd – this guitar NEEDS to be played by someone who loves it. Bid with confidence – I never sell junk!
